OOC: not everyone left the Dark Avian, Switchblade is still there, 
Dead-End is there but he's pretty much out of commission (and 
being repaired by Switchblade), I think that rdahl will be able to tell 
you who else is at the base still, but there aren't many.

::Astroblast/Drag Strip/Dead-End::

Astroblast sets down for a 3-points landing beside the Dark Avian. 
"Motormaster, we have arrived. The battle in south-east North 
America should commence shortly, we aren't that far away."
